---
title: Honey-Herb Pork & Grilled Courgette Salad with Lemon & Parmesan
description: Tonight’s juicy pork steak is oh-so-flavourful, glazed in an oregano-honey sauce that’s the perfect mix of sweet, sour and herbaceous. Paired with a fresh salad with smokey grilled courgette tossed through, this meal is fresh and effortlessly delicious—weeknight dining done right!

